tip.text: Food truck just opened this week. got the Spicey Ahi Bowl. Was so delicious and fairly priced with $13. Staff is very kind, too.
Great burger with very good meat. Try the Blue Hawaii Burger! Garlic fries were disappointing, while sweet potatoe fries where delicious.
Try out the Penang Curry and the Summer Rolls. Was delicious and fresh.
Great pizza!!!! Simply delicious. Try the zucchini pizza.
Wouldn't go here a second time. Burger was really fast food with low quality meat. I expected much more ...
Sushi was good an fresh. Try the UH roll. Big portion - I would stick to 2 rolls. Outside seating and friendly staff.
Very good, fresh and delicious food here. Poke was perfect and acme with kimchee. Need to sit outside and enjoy the plants
Great place. Great food. Great wine. should go for the 3 course menue with the wine pairing. Was delicious and is changing every week.
Wow was definitely worth the detour! The blue cheese burger was simply great, so was the Texas one. Fries were ok, but not special (maybe garlic fries are better 😉). Nice outdoor seating.
Delicious ice cream. Had two tastes and it was way too much :) used the rest for a milk shake. The sorbet was the best.
Ribeye and tilapia was very good. Diverse selection of vegetables aside, which seem to be seasonal (choose 1 out of 3). Buttermilk fries were kind of disappointing.
The carrot cake is much better than gingerbread. Have great stuff here.
Great food!! Traditional kitchen prepared in a modern way. As menu changes daily hard to tell what to chose. Chicken in claypot was delicious. Not as hot as Szechuan food is normally.
Food was ok. Fries are not good at all whereas Cioppino was very good.
Great place here. Good coffee and nice atmosphere. Can sit inside and outside.
Location very fancy, so are the guests. However cocktails could be better and service is lousy. Unfortunately the bar is not really profiting from the location...
Great sushi selection in a cosy environment. Need to try spicey tuna and pokemon!!!
Great cocktails. Try either the nikka whisky plain or the Commonwealth Tonic.
Took the "happier menu" with spicey chicken. Good taste for fast food and not like a normal burger. Curly fries are delicious but need some extra salt!
Great bar ( very nice door keeper) with great cocktails. Small menu but you can order everything you want. Fantastic whisky selection. Better reserve than you have access to a more secret room.
Good value for money. The daily dishes for lunch include a soup an small dessert. Service was lousy. Taste was very good.
Very good coffee and the porridge was great with a lot of fresh fruits.
Went there for Easter. Simply it is a great place. Very good and high quality food. Wine is relatively cheap. Try the rose. And of course the view is amazing.
Food was cold (Smoked Duck Joog) and service really slow. Even though it was not full, we waited 40minutes for our lunch!!!
Great place with a lot of seatings outside. Was very crowded for after work. But waiting was worth it. Try pizza "June" - bit spicey. Would rather go for a big one. Then the paste is thinner.
Great and fresh food. Service is very fast. Always full so better go either early or late for lunch.
Very cool bar with pool Billard and TV. Interesting mixture of people here. Very cheap for SF.Unfortunately when I was there kitchen was closed, but I was allowed to order UberEATS:)
Great and fresh vegetarian food. And interesting customer experience.
Coole und trendy Location, sehr voll - etwas zu voll sogar, man hat bei den bartischen kaum Platz für die Leute. Qualität der Speisen ist ok, jedoch nicht hervorstechend.
Was simple Great. Perfect service and fresh fish. Even though we hurdled with the Swedish names, the chef gave us good recommendations based on our wishes. Super!!!
Great and simple Swedish food. Mainly köttbullar (meat, fish or vegetarian). All biological! Great atmosphere, good price, very good quality)
Super sympa. Quelques verres de vin - très bonne qualité. Super repas (charcuterie, fromage). Super ambiance.
Was worth waiting for 2h to get a table for 3!!! Great pizza in nice and surprisingly quiet and stressless environment.
Fantastic cocktails in great and unique ambiance!
Best ice cream in town (and we ate a lot!). Must try: coconut ice cream. Lemon sorbet excellent. Pasta and salads looked delicious!!
Delicious food with different grades of spicey. Great dessert, too. Come here on "full moon party" (people try to reach a level of spicey). Great fun.
Delicious! Great and fresh food. Lovely staff!
Short menue for food and Drinks but very good quality. Go upstairs - it seems to be your grandmas living room with live concert!
I just ate the best fish&chips in my live!!! Enjoy the view from the terrace!
Great homemade pizza Italian style - thin and high quality products. Nice and friendly staff! Definitively go there again!
Very good fish and seafood. Super fresh. Good Price! We definitively go there again next time!
Menue (fish, salad/fries + wine/beer + Espresso) was good and tasty. Unfortunately fish was cold. We had the Impression to be in a served fast food restaurant :(
Super leckeres Wiener Schnitzel und für München auch mit moderaten Preisen. Uriges Restaurant immer voll
Great location in beautiful scenery. Very good food. Try the Whisky-mustard sauce served with the steak. Bar next to the restaurant with live band and less tourists ;)
Great cosy restaurant. Lot of fresh dishes. Great Taste. Must reserve in advance!
Small but sweet town with small Harbour. Definitively enjoy the view from McCaig's Tower!
Burgers very good. You must taste the Heverlee Lager - great beer
Essen sehr lecker. Coole, moderne Einrichtung. Leider eine lahme Bedienung. Tee, Essen und Bezahlung hat ewig gedauert. Leider auch nicht besonders freundlich :(
End of Royal mile (nearby Palace of Holyrood) nice exploring small streets and courts apart from Main Street!
Very good Food, meat, fresh vegetable. Nice people
Great dish of the Day! Big portions and very good taste!
Great view on and from the castle
Interestin church and beautiful cemetery - can be scary in the evening :)  and beautiful viele on the castle
Tolle Location trotz Lage im Touristen-Straße. Nur einheimische. Top Service!
